---
// AboutSection.astro
---

<section class="about-section section-padding">
  <div class="container grid grid-2">
    <!-- Left Column: Double Capsule Collage -->
    <div class="about-collage">
      <div class="capsule capsule-left">
        <img src="/images/about_airplane.png" alt="Aviation Cargo Logistics" />
      </div>
      <div class="capsule capsule-right">
        <img src="/images/about_truck.png" alt="Road Freight Delivery" />
      </div>
      <!-- Center Circular Stamp/Badge -->
      <div class="stamp-badge">
        <div class="stamp-inner">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-fast"></i>
          <span class="stamp-text">15+ Anos</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Content -->
    <div class="about-content">
      <span class="badge-tag">Quem Somos</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Líderes em Transporte e Armazenagem Inteligente</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Na pjholz, conectamos o mundo com eficiência operacional inigualável. Fundada sob o pilar de otimizar cadeias de suprimentos globais, nossa empresa investe em inovação e tecnologia de ponta para garantir que suas entregas cheguem no prazo, intactas e dentro do orçamento planejado.
      </p>

      <!-- Key Performance Indicators (Progress bars) -->
      <div class="about-kpis">
        <div class="kpi-item">
          <div class="kpi-info flex-between">
            <span class="kpi-name">Entregas no Prazo</span>
            <span class="kpi-value">99%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="kpi-bar-bg">
            <div class="kpi-bar-fill" style="width: 99%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi-item">
          <div class="kpi-info flex-between">
            <span class="kpi-name">Segurança de Carga</span>
            <span class="kpi-value">98%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="kpi-bar-bg">
            <div class="kpi-bar-fill" style="width: 98%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Checklist Grid -->
      <div class="feature-checklist grid grid-2">
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>
          <span>Transporte Seguro</span>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>
          <span>Suporte 24/7 Ativo</span>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>
          <span>Entrega Expressa</span>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>
          <span>Melhor Custo Logístico</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom Profile / Signature Card -->
      <div class="about-footer">
        <div class="ceo-profile">
          <img src="/images/ceo_avatar.png" alt="Polyana Souza" class="ceo-avatar" />
          <div class="ceo-info">
            <h4 class="ceo-name">Polyana Souza</h4>
            <span class="ceo-title">Fundadora & CEO</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Mais Detalhes</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);
  }

  /* Left Collage Styles */
  .about-collage {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    height: 450px;
  }

  .capsule {
    width: 45%;
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  .capsule img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .capsule:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.08);
  }

  .capsule-left {
    transform: translateY(-20px);
  }

  .capsule-right {
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }

  /* Center Badge Stamp */
  .stamp-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border: 6px solid var(--color-bg-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: 10;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .stamp-badge:hover {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1) rotate(15deg);
  }

  .stamp-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .stamp-inner i {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stamp-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Right Content Styles */
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Progress bars */
  .about-kpis {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .kpi-info {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .kpi-bar-bg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 6px;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-light);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .kpi-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 1s ease-in-out;
  }

  /* Feature list */
  .feature-checklist {
    gap: 1rem 2rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .checklist-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .checklist-item i {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Footer CEO & CTA button */
  .about-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ceo-profile {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .ceo-avatar {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .ceo-name {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .ceo-title {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-collage {
      height: 380px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .about-collage {
      height: 300px;
    }
    
    .stamp-badge {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
    }
    
    .stamp-inner i {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .stamp-text {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
    }

    .about-footer {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
